_page\">Modify a web page</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Safely_inserting_external_content_into_a_page\">Insert external content</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Sharing_objects_with_page_scripts\">Share objects with page scripts</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Add_a_button_to_the_toolbar\">Add a button to the toolbar</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Implement_a_settings_page\">Implement a settings page</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Working_with_the_Tabs_API\">Work with the Tabs API</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Work_with_the_Bookmarks_API\">Work with the Bookmarks API</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Work_with_the_Cookies_API\">Work with the Cookies API</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Work_with_contextual_identities\">Work with contextual identities</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Interact_with_the_clipboard\">Interact with the clipboard</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Build_a_cross_browser_extension\">Build a cross-browser extension</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Firefox_differentiators\">Firefox differentiators</a></summary>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details open=\"\">\n        <summary>JavaScript APIs</summary>\n        <ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/Browser_support_for_JavaScript_APIs\">Browser support for JavaScript APIs</a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/bookmarks\">bookmarks</a></li><li class=\"webextension-api-sidebar\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/commands\">commands</a><ol></ol></li></ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n      <summary>Manifest keys</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json\">Introduction</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      <ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/commands\">commands</a></li></ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n     <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>Extension Workshop</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/develop/\">Develop</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/publish/\">Publish</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/manage/\">Manage</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://extensionworkshop.com/documentation/enterprise/\">Enterprise</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n    <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/Contact_us\"><strong>Contact us</strong></a></li>\n    <li class=\"toggle\">\n      <details>\n        <summary>Channels</summary>\n        <ol>\n          <li><a href=\"https://blog.mozilla.org/addons\">Add-ons blog</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://discourse.mozilla.org/c/add-ons\">Add-ons forum</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"https://chat.mozilla.org/#/room/%23addons:mozilla.org\">Add-ons chat</a></li>\n        </ol>\n      </details>\n    </li>\n  </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Verwenden Sie die Ausführungsbefehle der Benutzer, die Sie mit Hilfe des <a href=\"/en-US/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/commands\"><code>Schlüssels commands</code> der manifest.json</a> registriert haben.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"typen","title":"Typen","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"commands.command\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/commands/Command\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">commands.Command (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>Objekt, das einen Befehl repräsentiert. Es enthält die für den Befehl im <a href=\"/en-US/Add-ons/WebExtensions/manifest.json/commands\"><code>Schlüssel commands der </code>manifest.json</a> festgelegten Informationen.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"funktionen","title":"Funktionen","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"commands.getall\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/commands/getAll\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">commands.getAll (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>\n <p>Stellt alle registrierten Befehle für diese Erweiterung zur Verfügung.</p>\n </dd>\n <dt id=\"commands.reset\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/commands/reset\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">commands.reset (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>\n <p>Angegebene Befehlsbeschreibung und das Tastaturkürzel auf die im Manifest-Schlüssel angegebenen Werte zurücksetzen.</p>\n </dd>\n <dt id=\"commands.update\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/commands/update\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">commands.update (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>\n <p>Beschreibung oder Tastenkürzel des angegebenen Befehls ändern.</p>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ereignisse","title":"Ereignisse","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"commands.oncommand\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/commands/onCommand\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">commands.onCommand (en-US)</a></dt>\n <dd>\n <div id=\"sect2\">Wird ausgelöst, wenn ein Befehl mit Hilfe seines zugewiesenen Tastenkürzels ausgeführt wird.</div>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"webextensions.api.commands","dataURL":"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/commands/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example_extensions","title":"Example extensions","isH3":false,"content":"<ul><li><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/webextensions-examples/tree/master/commands\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">commands</a></li></ul><p></p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect3\"><strong>Danksagungen</strong>\n\n<p>Diese API basiert auf der API <a href=\"https://developer.chrome.com/extensions/commands\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\"><code>chrome.commands</code></a> von Chromium.</p>\n\n<p>Die Kompatibilitätsdaten von Microsoft Edge werden von der Microsoft Corporation bereitgestellt und stehen hier unter der Lizenz Creative Commons Attribution 3.0 United States.</p>\n</div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Typen","id":"typen"},{"text":"Funktionen","id":"funktionen"},{"text":"Ereignisse","id":"ereignisse"},{"text":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität"},{"text":"Example extensions","id":"example_extensions"}],"summary":"Verwenden Sie die Ausführungsbefehle der Benutzer, die Sie mit Hilfe des Schlüssels commands der manifest.json registriert haben.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"commands","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"commands","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"commands","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"commands","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/mozilla/add-ons/webextensions/api/commands","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/mozilla/add-ons/webextensions/api/commands/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Mozilla","title":"Mozilla"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons","title":"Add-ons"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions","title":"WebExtensions"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API","title":"JavaScript APIs"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Mozilla/Add-ons/WebExtensions/API/commands","title":"commands"}],"pageTitle":"commands - Mozilla | MDN","noIndexing":false}}